{"tid":1857900,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《緊急》醫護手足做晒野，大陸文宣行動po呢？","createTime":"2020-02-02T11:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T11:50:39.000Z","uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4406fc0c8ccd7adae9d6db6e36336a1b25059d2a","tid":1857900,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"醫護手足已經表明罷工，但大陸討論區提都無提，完全平行時空，我地係時候做野，大家微博好wechat大陸人好小粉紅好，總之用盡任何方法揚俾大陸人聽香港醫護大罷工，落香港醫都係死路一條，唔好要醫護苦心白癈，更加唔使望柒婆會封關，佢會面都唔肯，就算真係大三罷成功都唔會理你，我地而家淨係可以靠自己咋，快做野啦香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f86a091b8e0c1519254f303f86857376cd2c04","tid":1857900,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"《天滅中共賦》<br />\n<br />\n共黨臣民 作惡多端<br />\n外侵諸邦 內屠義士<br />\n赤匪所至 寸草不生<br />\n禍國殃民 血債累累<br />\n習妖維尼 逆天而行<br />\n自立為帝 天怒人怨<br />\n庚子伊始 天譴將臨<br />\n大仙報夢 國運已盡<br />\n共黨治下 必有七患<br />\n正月武肺 播毒中原<br />\n二月流感 飛禽盡亡<br />\n三月地震 血流成河<br />\n四月豬瘟 百物騰升<br />\n五月飢荒 易子而食<br />\n六月內戰 析骸而爨<br />\n七月水災 長江決堤<br />\n炎共將亡 水德當立<br />\n歲在庚子 天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCW3BCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCW3BCS.jpg&h=64a71671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34e323dace68b9e5fd36f5cfa54f129b10234133","tid":1857900,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"P牌出po無人理"},{"pid":"ca8b2e07c27e7954bf952cf6b14ae237c27d7f69","tid":1857900,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"33bce71a54a5dadc82379d8f3293fa865bee583d","tid":1857900,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"3cb2de358b7ce233e2d43ccb62ee7066741